The paper focuses on neural networks-based pattern recognition systems for mobile and embedded applications, specifically using event-based visual input. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE) categories. The application of the system is for robotic tasks, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) category. The paper also discusses the challenges of training asynchronous neural networks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
